snippet.textDisplay:
"Forgetting my being in a trance I go  
Lending words to my heart, I let my heart, I let my feelings flow 
All the adulation from this world 
Still does not resolve my woes 
If all my wishes were to come true 
What would be left in the world to do
My destiny is beyond my control
I always let my heart know."
What a beautifully lyrical song about life! At first, I thought it was a love song, but thanks to the caption, I realized its deep philosophical meaning. Never thought a song with such profound wisdom could be this mesmerizing. Truly beautiful!
